creator: AABB Gold Token
descriptionHtml:
The leading blockchain wallet for all crypto coins and tokens, including: BTC, ETH, LTC, and AABBG.

Instantaneous AABB Gold (AABBG), Bitcoin (BTC), Ethereum (ETH), and altcoin transactions with the AABB Wallet.

Pick and use the world’s best blockchain wallet. Instant crypto transactions and anonymous internal transactions allow you to store your digital assets securely and send crypto funds instantly. Why wait many minutes when you can receive a Bitcoin transaction in seconds?

Send and Receive Crypto by SMS or Email
Send crypto with the just a touch! Select the contact from your phone and send them your cryptocurrency funds within the AABB Wallet.

Complete Anonymity
With the secure AABB Wallet, all your Bitcoin, Ethereum, AABB Gold, and other cryptocurrency transactions are hidden from the public. With our wallet, third parties have no way of seeing what you’re doing with your digital assets. Keep your cryptocurrency transactions private.

The Best Security!
AABB Wallet is designed to protect you against thieves and hackers, while allowing you to manage your funds easily. Your digital assets are secured with the AABB Wallet. Backup 6-word passphrase and AABB Wallet asks for your PIN Code every time you open your cryptocurrency wallet and make transactions.

You Have Full Control!
AABB Wallet never tracks, holds, or accesses your crypto - you are in complete control of your wallet. If necessary, restore your cryptocurrency wallet on any device with your 6-word passphrase.

Over 20 Cryptocurrencies Supported
Easily store all your crypto coins in one efficient blockchain wallet. AABB Wallet acts as a Bitcoin wallet, Ethereum wallet, Ethereum Classic wallet, Litecoin wallet, Dash wallet, Tether (USDT) wallet, and a wallet for the gold-backed AABB Gold (AABBG)!

Low Transaction Fees
When withdrawing cryptocurrencies such as Ethereum, Bitcoin, Litecoin, and other digital assets, AABB Wallet provides low transaction fees.

Take Part in our Referral Program
Quickly grow your crypto portfolio with our ongoing Referral Program! Earn commission every time your referral makes a transaction on AABB Wallet

Are you a Business Owner? Setup Loyalty Programs
Increase your customer conversion rate! Any seller or business can configure their own loyalty program. Use the program to incentivize customers to purchase products with the cryptocurrency wallet.

All Features of AABB Wallet:

- Anonymous internal transactions. Transaction history hidden from the public
- Send and receive crypto instantly with instant P2P, B2C, and B2B transactions
- Send crypto by social networks, email or any messenger
- Send crypto by QR Code, iTransfer, and by address
- Sophisticated security including PIN Code protection
- Open multiple accounts of the same currency: BTC, ETH, AABBG, LTC, and all other supported currencies
- Safely participate in ICO’s and TGE’s by storing multiple cryptocurrencies in AABB Wallet
- Low withdrawal fees
- Loyalty Program for businesses
- Map displaying businesses that use crypto
- Easy-to-use Referral Program. Refer and earn!
- Full account control. AABB Wallet never holds or accesses funds

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Updated KYC form, implemented instructions for the uploading of documents.
- Updated BCH Node.
- Minor bug fixes.
- Improved User Interface.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
The KYC form has been updated with additional fields, according to additional KYC/AML regulations. The KYC form is divided into several steps, with the User Interface (UI) being further optimized for user ease of use. Hints have also been added.

The Deposit and Withdraw pages have been optimized, increasing the speed of loading information by 18%.

The Merchant API Key, previously open to anyone, has been updated to be closed and is only accessible with a PIN Code/Password.

Instantaneous AABB Gold (AABBG), Bitcoin (BTC), Ethereum (ETH), and altcoin transactions with the AABB Wallet.

Pick and use the world’s best blockchain wallet. Instant crypto transactions and anonymous internal transactions allow you to store your digital assets securely and send crypto funds instantly. Why wait many minutes when you can receive a Bitcoin transaction in seconds?

Send and Receive Crypto by SMS or Email with iTransfer
Send crypto with the just a touch! Select the contact from your phone and send them your cryptocurrency funds within the AABB Wallet.

Complete Anonymity
With the secure AABB Wallet, all your Bitcoin, Ethereum, AABB Gold, and other cryptocurrency transactions are hidden from the public. With our wallet, third parties have no way of seeing what you’re doing with your digital assets. Keep your cryptocurrency transactions private.

The Best Security!
AABB Wallet is designed to protect you against thieves and hackers, while allowing you to manage your funds easily. Your digital assets are secured with the AABB Wallet. Backup 6-word passphrase and AABB Wallet asks for your PIN Code every time you open your cryptocurrency wallet and make transactions.

You Have Full Control!
AABB Wallet never tracks, holds, or accesses your crypto - you are in complete control of your wallet. If necessary, restore your cryptocurrency wallet on any device with your 6-word passphrase.

Over 20 Cryptocurrencies Supported
Easily store all your crypto coins in one efficient blockchain wallet. AABB Wallet acts as a Bitcoin wallet, Ethereum wallet, Ethereum Classic wallet, Litecoin wallet, Dash wallet, Tether (USDT) wallet, and a wallet for the gold-backed AABB Gold (AABBG)!

Low Transaction Fees
When withdrawing cryptocurrencies such as Ethereum, Bitcoin, Litecoin, and other digital assets, AABB Wallet provides low transaction fees.

Take Part in our Referral Program
Quickly grow your crypto portfolio with our ongoing Referral Program! Earn commission every time your referral makes a transaction on AABB Wallet

Are you a Business Owner? Setup Loyalty Programs
Increase your customer conversion rate! Any seller or business can configure their own loyalty program. Use the program to incentivize customers to purchase products with the cryptocurrency wallet.

All Features of AABB Wallet:
- Anonymous internal transactions. Transaction history hidden from the public
- Send and receive crypto instantly with instant P2P, B2C, and B2B transactions
- Send crypto by social networks, email or any messenger
- Send crypto by QR Code, iTransfer, and by address
- Sophisticated security including PIN Code protection
- Open multiple accounts of the same currency: BTC, ETH, AABBG, LTC, and all other supported currencies
- Safely participate in ICO’s and TGE’s by storing multiple cryptocurrencies in AABB Wallet
- Low withdrawal fees, no deposit fees
- Loyalty Program for businesses
- Map displaying businesses that use crypto
- Easy-to-use Referral Program. Refer and earn!
- Full account control. AABB Wallet never holds or accesses funds
